# Snapshot: code/booleans

## Case 01

### Source: `test/tmp_fs/code.frog`

```frog
true false && print
```

### Run

Command:

```text
py -m frog run test/tmp_fs/code.frog
```

Output:

```text
[PRINT] BOOL():False@test/tmp_fs/code.frog:1:12
```

### Build

Command:

```text
py -m frog -l WARN build -r test/tmp_fs/code.frog
```

Output:

```text
[CMD] gcc test/tmp_fs/code.c -o test/tmp_fs/code.exe
[CMD] test/tmp_fs/code.exe
[STDOUT]:
false

```

